<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/43526399-assaph-mehr"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1596954981i/43526399._UY100_CR3,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
