        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1415395996" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2108813077598491923">[Editorial Review] This is a story of Togas, Dagger, and Magic - the book I always wanted to read. It balances my favourite genres of historical mysteries, ancient Rome and fantasy. <br/><br/>The best compliment I got was from one of my beta readers:<br/><blockquote>
  <i><br/>This book gave me a ‘book-hangover’ - I could not get my head out of the world of Felix for days after finishing it!<br/></i>
</blockquote><br/><br/>I hope you will enjoy reading it as much as I enjoyed writing it.</span>

