<div id="review_1562459522" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1562459522" />
    <a title="Abbie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7358815-abbie"><img alt="Abbie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1547764466p2/7358815.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1562459522?book_show_action=true">Feb 27, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Abbie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Abbie" href="/user/show/7358815-abbie">Abbie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/26867372-murder-in-absentia">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1562459522" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1350210111120575893">Murder in Absentia is a fantastic blend of history, mystery, and magic. Travel back in time to an ancient Roman setting with the murder of a young man, a gritty detective not afraid to get his hands dirty, and brilliant plot filled with action and adventure. Witty, vivid, and very well-written, this book is one you won’t regret picking up. Fans of Tolkien, the Dresden Files, and the Remy Chandler series are going to love it. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


